  "text": "Thus it is clear that in order to have the improved regularity \"it is only necessary for the part of Ω that has divergence to be anti-symmetric\" as has been noted previously: [CITATION_1] and [CITATION_2] . We also point out that there have been further generalisations of this type of theorem in different directions -the interested reader should consult the works of Roger Moser [CITATION_3] and Armin Schikorra [CITATION_4] .",
